upturn in the second half and did not foresee any dividend payment for the
year. The last payment was in 1988.
Turnover amounted to Pounds 25.3m (Pounds 24.6m) and operating profits to
Pounds 941,000 (Pounds 21,000).
Earnings per share worked through at 3.78p (6.26p losses).
