FT  16 JUN 92 / Observer: Telling friends
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Offers are already landing on Slobodan Milosevic's desk just in case the
Serbian president could be persuaded to step down.
US congresswoman Helen Bentley saw the president in Belgrade recently and
