<HEADLINE>
FT  16 JUN 92 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
JOHANNESBURG's industrial index closed sharply lower ahead of the start of
the ANC's demonstrations against the government, losing 68 to 4,522. The
overall index fell 21 to 3,688 while the gold index was 34 higher at 1,147.
