FT  16 JUN 92 / Beer duty change
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A NEW SYSTEM for charging duty on beer will be introduced on April 1 next
year. Duty will be assessed on the volume and strength of beer and be
payable when it leaves registered breweries or bond. Under the present
system, introduced in 1880, duty is charged at the pre-fermentation stage.
