Investment (Ynm)
  State Industry          2,032    4,386    7,201    9,441      31.0
  Agriculture               158      111      211      298      41.0
Grain Output (ton m)      21.25    25.14    26.93    27.30         -
  Rice                    19.43    23.39    25.17    25.34         -
