FT  16 JUN 92 / World News In Brief: Win for Germany
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Germany beat Scotland 2-0 in their group two match, boosting their hopes of
a semi-final place in the European football championship. Netherlands and
the CIS drew 0-0.
