<TEXT>
'Where d'you get that lot then?', a hungry vampire demanded, meeting its
mate flying home with blood all over its mouth.
Beckoning, it turned round and led the way for a short while before asking:
'Do you see that big tree straight ahead?' The other nodded.
'Well, I didn't,' it added.
